<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢١٢٧ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَبِإِسْنَادِهِ عَنْ عَامِرٍ قَالَ:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«رَأَيْتُ عَلَى الْحُسَيْنِ بْنِ عَلِيٍّ جُبَّةَ خَزٍّ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>